metadata.name: Transmuting
metadata.description:
tl:dr 
My AI sidekick and I rocked this out like a garage band that hit a groove and jammed. I could linger watching these trippy morphs all day, you too? Ok, pick up your jaw, make a bid and enjoy the ride with me!

The anxious artist inside me wants you to know (sorry she blah blah blah's a lot):  
This mesmerizing art piece is a testament to the power of AI. It combines remixed seed images of a stormy beach and an otherworldly space-time juncture to create a captivating blend of chaos and mystery. The resulting final gif-style video portrays a younger girl transforming into an older one, with delicate fairy-style lights and space transitions between each image.

This transformation adds an intriguing layer to the artwork, conveying the theme of innocence and mystery in the midst of life's unanswered questions. The seamless morphing of images creates a dreamlike journey through time, inviting you to contemplate the passage of time and the changes it brings. The ethereal atmosphere and enduring sense of mystery create a thought-provoking and visually stunning experience for anyone who views it.
